Takerovoj?

176
00:12:16,066 --> 00:12:18,091
Napred.

177
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:25,848
Donela sam tikete za pobednike,
gospodine Mors.

178
00:12:26,058 --> 00:12:29,559
